th%E1%BA%A1ch-minh/poem-LvAIPeNKA5xF-9ycVsrvjw">Toạ thạch minh - 座右銘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Vi%E1%BB%87n/author-j-BevTHvR1oyXw66IODG8A">Thôi Viện</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91i-n%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-H5s_djxQcWKh3qzW5QeJBA">Tối năng hành - 最能行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Mai-Pha/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-mai-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-zSPC6PVp1fcZemvavfPMhQ">Tuyết mai kỳ 1 - 雪梅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Mai-Pha/author-RsrtOLmUMIuICsXh29zWQw">Lư Mai Pha</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%E1%BB%8Dng-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-WqJvkXl9a2ORHiddnRzsKw">Vọng Tương Sơn tự - 望湘山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
